                            <comment id="13708126" author="hiranya" created="Sun, 14 Jul 2013 21:31:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch has been committed with some modifications. There was a race condition that I had to take care of. Fix has been tested with sample 800 (REST APIs) and also sample 150 (proxy services returning WSDLs for ?wsdl request). This is good to go.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
